{"tid":1754910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆必須修補同進化：包括區政指引素人","createTime":"2019-11-25T11:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T20:02:58.000Z","uid":150625,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"96cd8c7a1ff21c7dd891349d777e1989127014db","tid":1754910,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"手足後勤文宣既戰線係選舉後絕對未完 <br />\n多謝對家幫手清左連儂牆舊資訊<br />\n大家可以瘋狂貼新野<br />\n暴政、黑警知法犯法等事實之餘<br />\n請大家進化貼下該區區政期望<br />\n指導各區政治素人應該做咩<br />\n同時滴水穿石connect/維繫其他街坊<br />\n相信每個區選素人都明白今次唔係佢地既勝利<br />\n會好好留意大家既聲音<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be881cd5a9d583c7979fdaea78f5038648eff6b","tid":1754910,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> be humble"},{"pid":"ae5767b547546bd4a02cacb1302e8993d0972624","tid":1754910,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> be humble"},{"pid":"106e87a5c9acac007adbabf42cf57792c6664105","tid":1754910,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> be humble"},{"pid":"2bb109778389bdf37615b353722e72c3f28f9167","tid":1754910,"uid":191613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bea7d0e05bd2f130b6e0a7b97339273625c53aa9","tid":1754910,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> be humble"